cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia7' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RF simulator model name to an invalid enum 'invalid_model' will cause RF simulation initialization errors and prevent proper signal processing in the DU.
du.explanation_zh: 將 RF 模擬器模型名稱設定為無效的枚舉值 'invalid_model' 會導致 RF 模擬初始化錯誤，並阻止 DU 中的正確訊號處理。
